gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己顧自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要勇武先得㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時就可以向犧牲者致敬，過一年又可以懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a65742a890550e0ce0a3d78fe37fe89ed200a0e","tid":115934,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個司機唔緊急煞停，車箱入面又逼到沙甸魚咁，點走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊係月台影相果啲<br />\n<br />\n如果係隧道急停，得車頭車尾有位走，兩邊太窄落唔到路軌，燒死都未走到<br />\n<br />\n但衝去下一個站既話，有四十度門一齊開，一齊衝上路面，一定快過係隧道走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然金鐘去尖咀路程2-3分鐘，但係一恐慌起上黎要等到下個站先走得甩，就好容易人踩人，今次好彩冇踩死人唔代表下單冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce5b0ce56bb79a9dcfa6b71bf564fb9014e233b","tid":115934,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前英皇高層Kitty媽由金鐘到達尖沙嘴落車，「月台廣播已經話：『本站發生嚴重事故，大家即刻離開。』但香港人好奇怪，大家都喺度等下一班車，可能大家冇意識起火，以為只係故障，月台再廣播叫大家離開，我上到大堂見到警察到。我冇行去車頭睇，見唔到火人」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人呢幾年不斷俾d提示轟炸，緊握扶手、胡楓提提你、波板糖人，到真係有事就麻木曬<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母！"},{"pid":"c58d7b87ca874f8d86634ea5a4dd41e7997ce631","tid":115934,"uid":83835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"消防員？行開啦 連登仔乜撚都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90849893620dfcb4499314ee37f159d4f20b960","tid":115934,"uid":29818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"Co2同乾粉滅火筒好似係乜火都用得<img src=\"/assets